{"tid":811464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【放題店陰招】廚師爆料｜放題店四招令你回唔到本 刺身上得快都有伏？","createTime":"2018-09-08T22:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T10:49:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"886e9252f35fd97961efc0f6d70d9a953363d0ee","tid":811464,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T22:37:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rwg3yirC_dk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Drwg3yirC_dk&d=EeaBWpaP66fxj6hkiHlU7TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4c428598\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rwg3yirC_dk</a><br />\n極受香港人歡迎的日式放題餐廳，基本上每次有傳媒報道都把着眼點放在回本食物上。事實上大部分客人上門亦會抱着要回本的心態。但試想想，如果每個人都能回本，餐廳早就關門大吉了。一位曾在放題餐廳工作的廚師也爆料，餐廳有不少方法令客人提早吃飽，變相少柯打了其他食物，餐廳自然賺得多了。到底這些陰招是甚麼？"},{"pid":"406931f3aadb2fe44e277b6579f4615d6de88f80","tid":811464,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T22:41:07.000Z","msg":"我去親食放題都回晒本，啲侍應細細聲商量想諗辦法令我以後唔好再去<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bwJgnS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bwJgnS</a>"},{"pid":"b7af7dbb6d234c9f0dabf1e3fcfc74b5b18daf8c","tid":811464,"uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T22:52:11.000Z","msg":"食到回本&hellip;&hellip;已經係虐待自己身體啦"},{"pid":"d2b5a55b09a2284a95e449b9590afb2262ab58ac","tid":811464,"uid":202051,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T22:54:27.000Z","msg":"點樣叫回本? 用呢種心態食野嘅人根本就唔應該去食放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地做生意會諗個方法比你賺番佢錢架咩? 都戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ff64ef930f5a114a3070fde9a57b7babed6a1e","tid":811464,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b7af7dbb6d234c9f0dabf1e3fcfc74b5b18daf8c","tid":811464,"uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T22:52:11.000Z","msg":"食到回本&hellip;&hellip;已經